## Before opening or updating a pull request

Run all four commands from the `hypha-web` root. All must pass. Fix any failures before pushing.

```bash
pnpm turbo run check-types --filter=web
pnpm run format:check
pnpm run verify:messages
pnpm run check:matrix-sdk
```

If `format:check` fails, run `pnpm run format` to auto-fix, then re-run `format:check` to confirm.

If the branch includes new or changed migration files under `packages/storage-postgres/migrations/`, also run:

```bash
pnpm run migrate
```

Do not open the PR until all commands exit with code 0.
